      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer les dérivées partielles $\\dpa{V}{r}$ et $\\dpa{V}{\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer les dérivées partielles <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{r}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "932abb24-eece-4595-9d28-5d1a740d9f8d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $(r,\\theta) \\in \\mathcal{D}_V$, on a \n\t\t\t\\[ \\dpa{V}{r} = -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta, \\ \\ \\dpa{V}{\\theta} = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\]",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((r,\\theta) \\in\n\\mathcal{D}_V\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\dpa{V}{r} =\n-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta, \\ \\ \\dpa{V}{\\theta} =\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "979e8b61-f2e9-44b5-9b7a-13aaefca870c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer les dérivées partielles secondes $\\dpsp{V}{r}$, $\\dpa{V}{\\theta}$ et $\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer les dérivées partielles secondes <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpsp{V}{r}\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{\\theta}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c05a698c-a592-49fc-9d68-0a0fca0ea60a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $(r,\\theta) \\in \\mathcal{D}_V$, on a\n\t\t\t$$\\begin{align*} \n\t\t\t\\dpsp{V}{r} &= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta \\right] = \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n\t\t\t\\dpsp{V}{\\theta} &= \\dpa{}{\\theta}\\left[ -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n\t\t\t\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta} &= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = \\frac{2}{r^3}\\sin\\theta\n\t\t\t\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((r,\\theta) \\in\n\\mathcal{D}_V\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\dpsp{V}{r} &amp;= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta\n\\right] = \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n            \\dpsp{V}{\\theta} &amp;= \\dpa{}{\\theta}\\left[\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n            \\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta} &amp;= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = \\frac{2}{r^3}\\sin\\theta\n            \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a2f3aa16-65d0-4138-ab15-2270b1585e4f",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire que $$\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]  = 0.$$",
        "html": "<p>En déduire que <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r}\n\\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta\n\\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]  = 0.\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "48706bf2-a8f1-4d58-a616-ec60a07fb1c6",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On a\n\t\t\t\\begin{eqnarray*}\n\t\t\t\t\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]\n\t\t\t\t&= \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r \\dpa{V}{r} + r^2 \\dpsp{V}{r} \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} + \\sin\\theta \\dpsp{V}{\\theta} \\right] \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&= \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r (-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta) + r^2 \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta) + \\sin\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta) \\right] \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&= \\frac{\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta}{r^2}(-4+ 6-1-1) \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&= 0\n\t\t\\end{eqnarray*}",
        "html": "<p>On a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n                \\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  +\n\\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]\n                &amp;= \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r \\dpa{V}{r} + r^2 \\dpsp{V}{r}\n\\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} + \\sin\\theta\n\\dpsp{V}{\\theta} \\right] \\\\\n                &amp;= \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r (-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta) +\nr^2 \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta\n(-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta) + \\sin\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta)\n\\right] \\\\\n                &amp;= \\frac{\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta}{r^2}(-4+ 6-1-1) \\\\\n                &amp;= 0\n        \n\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
